steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT036DatetimePickerPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT036DatetimePickerPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT036DatetimePickerPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT036DatetimePickerPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "Date Time Picker" in Search popup with sub menu "Form" to preview mobile editor
When I toggle on item value "JIT036DatetimePickerPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I select item value "DatePicker" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I select dropdown field label "Date Mode" of header "DateTime Picker" with value "Date"
